text.tspan: Based on the expert estimates and index by V-Dem , weighted by countries' populations. It combines
information on suffrage, the freedom and fairness of elections, freedoms of association and expression, as well
as the extent to which citizens can engage in regional and local government, civil society organizations and
direct democracy. It ranges from 0 to 1 (most democratic).
